# Mapbox-Assist  [![License: CC BY-NC 4.0](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-CC%20BY--NC%204.0-lightgrey.svg)](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/)

Work in progress ...

Wrapper to facilitate Mapbox functionality

Features when completed:
- fitting rotated and pitched maps
- adding & drawing routes, display route information & detailed elevation profile
- adding points of interest on the fly
- clickable features with pop-over information panel